text: Sylvanus Olympio was the first president of Togo. He served as Togo first president from 1961 to 1963. Unfortunately, he was assassinated. ==Bibliography== ===Books and Journals=== * ===Newspapers=== * * * * * * Category:Presidents of Togo Category:Prime ministers of Togo Category:1902 births Category:1963 deaths
